description:
Professional shaman Holly Million, who became Gnome's executive director in October, has evidently participated in a banishing ritual and will disappear from Gnome at the end of this month.

The post Poof! Shaman Holly Million, Gnome’s Executive Director Disappears on July 31 appeared first on FOSS Force.
title: Poof! Shaman Holly Million, Gnome’s Executive Director Disappears on July 31
